%%{init: {"theme": "forest"}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as Serveur
    participant DB as SQLite

    C->>S: GET /api/v1/questions?theme_id=...&type=MCQ&level=3&page=1&limit=20<br/>Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
    S->>S: Authentification + Autorisation (admin)

    S->>S: Parser les query parameters de filtrage

    alt Filtres invalides (type inconnu, level hors 1-5, min > max, etc.)
        S-->>C: 400 INVALID_FILTER
    else Conflit level + level_min/level_max
        S-->>C: 400 INVALID_FILTER
    else Filtres valides
        opt theme_id présent
            S->>DB: Vérifier l'existence du thème
            alt Thème introuvable
                S-->>C: 400 INVALID_FILTER
            end
        end

        S->>DB: SELECT * FROM T_QUESTION_QST<br/>WHERE theme_id = ? AND type = ? AND level = ?<br/>AND time_limit BETWEEN ? AND ?<br/>AND points BETWEEN ? AND ?<br/>ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT ? OFFSET ?
        DB-->>S: Résultats filtrés
        S-->>C: 200 OK { data, page, limit, total }
    end
